<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلِلتَّفْصِيل <span class="c2">(ر: نَسَبٌ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَذْفُ الْمَمْسُوحِ بِالزِّنَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١١ - اخْتَلَفَ الْفُقَهَاءُ فِي حَدِّ قَاذِفِ الْمَمْسُوحِ بِالزِّنَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَذَهَبَ الْجُمْهُورُ إِلَى أَنَّهُ لاَ يُحَدُّ حَدَّ الْقَذْفِ، وَذَهَبَ الْحَنَابِلَةُ إِلَى أَنَّهُ يُحَدُّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلِلتَّفْصِيل <span class="c2">(ر: قَذْفٌ ف ٤٧)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مُمَوَّهٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> آنِيَّةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مُمَيِّزٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> تَمْيِيزٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
